Package: AirMonitoringInequality
Type: Project
Title: Inequality in Air Pollution Monitoring and Exposure: Evidence from Four Latin American Cities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bridget", "Hoffman", email = "bridgeth@iadb.org", role = "aut"),
    person("Patricio", "Dominguez", email = "pdomingr@uc.cl", role = "aut"),
    person("Maria Paula", "Medina", email = "mpmedina@ucdavis.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Marcos Paulo", "Correia", email = "marcospaulorcorreia@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: >
    Replication package for air pollution analysis across four metropolitan
    areas in Latin America. Covers data download, processing, and
    visualization of ground monitoring station data integrated with
    satellite-derived sources (MERRA-2) and census geographies.
